{"type":"article","id":11950,"title":"【投诉】管理员 如火如荼 （原名：法拉儿）","uid":25792,"topics":[],"contents":"【被投诉用户】<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E5%A6%82%E7%81%AB%E5%A6%82%E8%8D%BC\">如火如荼</a><br>\n【被投诉理由】滥用管理员职权，观察，打压质疑郭文贵网友<br>\n【投诉要求】取消我的观察，对此管理员，管理权限进行观察。<br>\n【详情】<br>\n1. 此管理员为贵站挺郭一员大将，平时大家看帖子就知道。我说明了，我这是小号，就怕大号被此管理员赖上。此管理员说我复读：郭是不是骗子，6.5见分晓，我只说了2遍，这也叫复读么？其次，我举报的帖子看清楚，举报的那人对我和另外一个人进行人身攻击，这符合版规吧：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-185016\">https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-185016</a><br>\n2. 此管理员一天内连续限制了2名质疑郭的网友，取消了一名辱骂他人的挺郭者的观察。其中一名就是发了一个视频帖子，说如何远离现实生活中像郭这种人，就被她观察了，这不是故意碰瓷，找茬，这还是啥?<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://ftp.bmp.ovh/imgs/2020/01/b87141b09b4deba3.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://ftp.bmp.ovh/imgs/2020/01/b87141b09b4deba3.png</a>3. 对我之前多处质疑郭的评论，我已经和几位管理员讨论过，他们不认为我这是找茬，沟通后我已经表示日后不挑衅。具体：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/14735\">https://pincong.rocks/question/14735</a><br>\n4. 贵站挺郭的蚂蚁们多次辱骂，挑事，啥事情都没，我就压根就没理他们，就发表我的看法，就被观察，这种做法合理么？贵站倡导的公平和理 理性的原则去哪了，就因为某个管理层挺郭就可以随便打压言论自由？这种泄私愤的滥用管理权限，是不是应该质疑？<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-184577\">https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-184577</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-184577\">https://pincong.rocks/video/item_id-5920</a><br>\nhttps://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-184516<br>\nhttps://pincong.rocks/video/item_id-5925<br>\n<br>\n[url=https://pincong.rocks/people/miule236236][/url]<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/miule236236\">@miule236236</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%B7%A1%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%A7%E6%B3%95\">@中国网警巡查执法</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/waliesi\">@waliesi</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E7%96%AF%E7%8B%82%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3\">@疯狂习近平</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/magrabee\">@magrabee</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/HelicopterZ\">@HelicopterZ</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/rgjdwte\">@rgjdwte</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/Tashkent\">@Tashkent</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/en010272\">@en010272</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/nmff\">@nmff</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E9%9F%AD%E8%8F%9C%E5%9C%B0%E9%87%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B9%E8%91%B1\">@韭菜地里一根葱</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/Ambulance\">@Ambulance</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/InspectorBen\">@InspectorBen</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E5%B8%81%E5%9C%88%E5%A5%87%E8%91%A98964\">@币圈奇葩8964</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/killreddragon\">@killreddragon</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B2%A2%E6%B0%91\">@江沢民</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/pc6650\">@pc6650</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/vvgvv1\">@vvgvv1</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/2%E6%A0%B72simple\">@2样2simple</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/trtrtr2\">@trtrtr2</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/No_pains\">@No_pains</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E8%8D%86%E6%A3%98%E4%B9%8B%E5%BF%83\">@荆棘之心</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/kcyx2184\">@kcyx2184</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E7%B5%82%E5%B0%87%E6%88%B0%E5%8B%9D%E6%AD%B8%E4%BE%86\">@正義終將戰勝歸來</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4\">@广场青年</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E4%BB%A4%E7%8B%90%E5%86%B2\">@令狐冲</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E9%B8%A1%E9%B8%A1\">@</a><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E7%AA%92%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F\">窒息中求生</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/yogafire\">@yogafire</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/silaoye\">@silaoye</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/anonymousLiu\">@anonymousLiu</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pincong